Required packages
=================
CMake: sudo apt-get install cmake
ccmake: sudo apt-get install cmake-curses-gui
sudo apt-get install build-essential freeglut3-dev xorg-dev libglu1-mesa-dev
sudo apt-get install libxi-dev libxrandr-dev

